caption.p: Titre of ZIKV in midguts and salivary glands of wMel-Sg and WT Ae. aegypti at days 6, 9 and 13 post-infectious blood meal. ZIKV level is both midguts and salivary glands were determined using viral titration assay and expressed as Log 10TCI 50/mL. Bars denote median viral titres. *** denotes significant difference at P<0.05 by Mann-Whitney test. Each point represents an individual midgut/salivary glands.
